---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">EV Tracker</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Open source project tracking the adoption of electric vehicles in France and Europe. visualizing market trends with precision.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">Links</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Methodology</a></li>
          <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Data Sources</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
          Data sourced from official government publications and aggregated for easy consumption.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8 text-center text-sm text-gray-400">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} EV Tracker. Licensed under GPL.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
